{"type":"text","timestamp":1773245535857,"sessionID":"ses_3225b067cffelwLK8Sy8mv6BSq","part":{"id":"prt_cddab1746002YbfkWMzJgfX9zC","sessionID":"ses_3225b067cffelwLK8Sy8mv6BSq","messageID":"msg_cddab0545001xoLVzumXGHDkqF","type":"text","text":"## Goal\n\nRetrofit `--output json` support across all CLI commands in the `wombo` project. The feature was only implemented for some `features` subcommands (list, add, set-status, show). It needs to be added to: `features check`, `features archive`, and all operational commands (`status`, `launch`, `verify`, `merge`, `cleanup`, `retry`, `resume`, `upgrade`).\n\n## Instructions\n\n- **Branch:** `feature/json-output-complete` (already checked out)\n- **Working directory:** `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete`\n- Human-friendly text output MUST remain the default\n- JSON schemas should be consistent with existing features subcommand patterns (use `output()`, `outputMessage()`, `outputError()` from `src/lib/output.ts`)\n- Use conventional commits: `feat(json-output-complete):` scope\n- Commit after each logical unit of work (per subtask roughly)\n- Do NOT squash, do NOT push to remote, do NOT modify `.features.yml`\n- After all changes, run `bun run build` to verify\n- The spec defines 3 subtasks: (1) features check, (2) features archive, (3) all operational commands\n- The `OutputFormat` type is `\"text\" | \"json\"`, resolved via `resolveOutputFormat()` in `src/lib/output.ts`\n- For long-running commands (launch, resume), JSON mode should emit initial state and suggest polling `wombo status --output json` rather than entering monitoring loops\n\n## Discoveries\n\n- The output helpers are in `src/lib/output.ts`: `output(fmt, data, textRenderer)`, `outputMessage(fmt, msg, extra)`, `outputError(fmt, msg, exitCode)` — these handle JSON vs text rendering\n- The existing pattern: commands accept `outputFmt?: OutputFormat` in their options interface, default to `\"text\"` with `const fmt = opts.outputFmt ?? \"text\"`\n- `index.ts` is the CLI entry point that parses args and routes to command handlers. It already parses `--output`/`-o` into `args.outputFmt`\n- The `index.ts` needs to be updated to pass `outputFmt: args.outputFmt` to each command's options object\n- State types are in `src/lib/state.ts` — `WaveState`, `AgentState`, `AgentStatus`, `agentCounts()`\n- `printDashboard()` in `src/lib/ui.ts` renders the ANSI dashboard (text mode only)\n\n## Accomplished\n\n### Completed:\n1. **features check** — Added `outputFmt` to options, imports `output` from output.ts, emits `{ok, items_checked, errors, warnings, issues}` in JSON mode. ✅\n2. **features archive** — Added `outputFmt` to options, uses `output()`, `outputMessage()`, `outputError()`, emits `{archived, count}` / `{dry_run, archived, count}` in JSON mode. ✅\n3. **Committed** subtasks 1 & 2 as commit `172127f`. ✅\n\n### In Progress (all modified but NOT yet committed):\n4. **status** — Fully retrofitted. Emits `{active, wave_id, agents, counts, total}` in JSON mode. ✅\n5. **launch** — Retrofitted. Dry-run emits structured JSON. Non-dry-run emits wave creation state in JSON mode. ✅\n6. **verify** — Retrofitted. Emits `{verified, count, wave_id}` in JSON mode. ✅\n7. **merge** — Retrofitted. Emits `{merged, count, failed, wave_id, pushed}` in JSON mode. ✅\n8. **cleanup** — Retrofitted. Emits structured dry-run and cleanup results in JSON mode. ✅\n9. **retry** — Retrofitted. Emits structured JSON for dry-run and actual retry. ✅\n10. **resume** — Partially retrofitted (triage messages, interactive path done). ✅\n11. **upgrade** — Retrofitted but **HAS BUILD ERRORS** on lines 156 and 228. ⚠️\n\n### NOT yet done:\n- **Fix `installVersion` function** in `upgrade.ts` — it currently takes 1 arg `(tag: string)` but the updated `cmdUpgrade` calls it with 2 args `(tag, fmt)`. Need to update `installVersion` signature to accept `fmt` parameter and use it for JSON output.\n- **Update `index.ts`** to pass `outputFmt: args.outputFmt` to ALL operational command calls (status, launch, verify, merge, cleanup, retry, resume, upgrade). Currently only features check and archive have been updated in index.ts.\n- **Run `bun run build`** and fix any remaining type/build errors.\n- **Commit** the operational commands changes.\n\n## Relevant files / directories\n\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/index.ts` — CLI entry point, routes commands, needs `outputFmt` passed to all command options\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/lib/output.ts` — Output helpers (`output`, `outputMessage`, `outputError`, `OutputFormat`)\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/lib/state.ts` — Wave/Agent state types, `agentCounts()`\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/lib/ui.ts` — `printDashboard()`, text-only rendering\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/commands/features/check.ts` — ✅ Done (committed)\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/commands/features/archive.ts` — ✅ Done (committed)\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/commands/status.ts` — Modified, not committed\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/commands/launch.ts` — Modified, not committed\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/commands/verify.ts` — Modified, not committed\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/commands/merge.ts` — Modified, not committed\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/commands/cleanup.ts` — Modified, not committed\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/commands/retry.ts` — Modified, not committed\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/commands/resume.ts` — Modified, not committed\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/commands/upgrade.ts` — Modified, **has LSP errors on lines 156 and 228** (`installVersion` needs 2nd `fmt` param)\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/commands/features/list.ts` — Reference (already has JSON support)\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/commands/features/show.ts` — Reference (already has JSON support)\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/commands/features/add.ts` — Reference (already has JSON support)\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-json-output-complete/src/commands/features/set-status.ts` — Reference (already has JSON support)","time":{"start":1773245535855,"end":1773245535855}}}
